%N A394639 Start of exactly five even numbers that are totient numbers (A002202).
%e A394639 16, 18, 20, 22, and 24 are totient numbers but 14 and 26 are not, so 16 is a term.
%o A394639 (PARI) isok(k) = if (!(k%2), !istotient(k-2) && (sum(i=0, 4, istotient(k+2*i)) == 5) && !istotient(k+10)); \\ _Michel Marcus_, Mar 30 2026
